latestIgtvVideos.title: Lets get ready for Navratri 💃🏻
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hi guys, lets get ready for Navratri and see how we can create this look in 10 minutes ⌛️ I know this is not the most professional way of doing makeup but well this is how i do it and the outcome is how i wanted it to be. ☺️❤️
Also, guys please let me know if y’all would like to see some kind of a makeup look or a style video.🌈☺️ The following are the products i used in this video 
1. @neutrogena oil free facial moisturiser 
2. @diormakeup @dior  lip glow lipbalm (007, raspberry) 
3. @lovecolorbar  BB cream (vanilla cream) 
4. @maybelline  instant age rewind concealer (140, honey) 
5. @lovecolorbar  perfect match compact powder. 
6. @maybelline  colorshow blush (fresh coral)
7.  @lovecolorbar  black kajal 
8.  @makeuprevolution x @soph Extra spice palette 
8.  @maybelline  lash sensational mascara 
9.  @chamborgeneva extreme wear liquid lipstick (406)
.
@nykaabeauty  @mynykaa  @plixxo  @popxobeauty @nykaabeautybook
